---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const description =
  'Legal and acceptable-use notes for RedSec learning content.';
---

<BaseLayout title="Legal" description={description}>
  <section class="policy-page">
    <div class="container policy-wrap">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Legal and acceptable use</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        RedSec content is educational. It is not permission to test systems you
        do not own or operate without explicit authorization.
      </p>

      <h2>Authorized use only</h2>
      <p>
        Use the lessons, labs, and examples only in your own environment, in a
        CTF, or under a written scope where testing is allowed. You are
        responsible for understanding and following the rules that apply to your
        location, target, program, school, employer, or platform.
      </p>

      <h2>No professional advice</h2>
      <p>
        The material is provided for general learning. It is not legal advice,
        compliance advice, or a substitute for guidance from a qualified
        professional.
      </p>

      <h2>No warranty</h2>
      <p>
        The site is provided as-is. RedSec does not promise that content is
        complete, current, error-free, or suitable for a specific environment.
        Always validate techniques in a safe lab before relying on them.
      </p>

      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This learning site sets no cookies, ships no analytics, and makes no
        third-party requests from its pages. Progress, if any, is stored only on
        your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Responsible disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        If you find a vulnerability in a real system while learning, stop
        testing, preserve only necessary evidence, and follow the target
        owner's disclosure process.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page {
    padding-block: var(--space-24);
  }
  .policy-wrap {
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
  .policy-wrap h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
  }
</style>
